 73	```
 74	
 75	### 2. 启动服务器
 76	
 77	```bash
 78	# 自动检测并启动最佳运行时
 79	php think runtime:start
 80	
 81	# 指定运行时启动
 82	php think runtime:start swoole
 83	php think runtime:start frankenphp
 84	php think runtime:start reactphp
 85	php think runtime:start ripple
 86	
 87	# 自定义参数启动
 88	php think runtime:start swoole --host=127.0.0.1 --port=8080 --workers=8
 89	php think runtime:start frankenphp --port=8080 --workers=4
 90	php think runtime:start reactphp --host=0.0.0.0 --port=8080
 91	php think runtime:start ripple --host=0.0.0.0 --port=8080 --workers=4
 92	```
 93	
 94	### 3. 查看运行时信息
 95	
 96	```bash
 97	php think runtime:info
 98	```
